edin.voyager.jobs.shared.Title"},{"description":"GE Vernova is a planned purpose-built company on a mission to electrify the planet while simultaneously working to decarbonize it.\n\nIf we want our energy future to be different…we must be different.\n\nOur mission is embedded in our name. We retain our treasured legacy, “GE,” in our name as an enduring and hard-earned badge of quality and ingenuity. “Ver” / “verde” signal Earth’s verdant and lush ecosystems. “Nova,” from the Latin “novus,” nods to a new, innovative era of lower carbon energy that GE Vernova will help deliver.\n\nGE Vernova brings together GE’s portfolio of energy businesses including Power, Wind, Electrification and Digital businesses. With focus, GE Vernova is accelerating the path to more reliable, affordable, and sustainable energy, while helping our customers power economies and deliver the electricity that is vital to health, safety, security, and improved quality of life.\n\nTogether, we have The Energy to Change the World.","staffCount":54299,"viewerFollowingJobsUpdates":false,"entityUrn":"urn:li:fs_normalized_company:82315716","staffCountRange":{"start":10001,"$type":"com.linkedin.voyager.organization.shared.StaffCountRange"},"headquarter":null,"logo":{"image":{"$type":"com.linkedin.common.VectorImage","rootUrl":"https://media.licdn.com/dms/image/v2/D4E0BAQG3fXAI-jYu5A/company-logo_","artifacts":[{"width":200,"expiresAt":1744848000000,"fileIdentifyingUrlPathSegment":"200_200/company-logo_200_200/0/1681910638687/gevernova_logo?e=1744848000&v=beta&t=wo3WGml9HsDvJpm2VVwFeI3uMLMTFcUg9Zqgk6PY_Qg","$type":"com.linkedin.common.VectorArtifact","height":200},{"width":100,"expiresAt":1744848000000,"fileIdentifyingUrlPathSegment":"100_100/company-logo_100_100/0/1681910638687/gevernova_logo?e=1744848000&v=beta&t=QErHLiaH-CUVy0OHg8DrLbBOmMuSQReHdipq4yxjSJE","$type":"com.linkedin.common.VectorArtifact","height":100},{"width":400,"expiresAt":1744848000000,"fileIdentifyingUrlPathSegment":"400_400/company-lo